OL,3,CSensory garden to be built in tribute
OL,4,Cto six-year-old killed by mother
OL,6,FA six-year-old boy, killed by his
OL,7,Fmother in Swansea, has been described
OL,8,Fas "bright and intelligent" by a
OL,9,Fparent who spoke with him just weeks
OL,10,Fbefore his death.
OL,12,FThe body of Alexander Zurawski was
OL,13,Fdiscovered at his home on Cwm Du Close
OL,14,Fin Gendros in August last year.
OL,16,FHis mother, Karolina Zurawska, 41,
OL,17,Fpleaded guilty to the manslaughter of
OL,18,Fher son on the grounds of diminished
OL,19,Fresponsibility. She also pleaded
OL,20,Fguilty to the attempted murder of her
OL,21,Ffather, Krysztof Siwy.
