OL,3,CSensory garden to be built in tribute
OL,4,Cto six-year-old killed by mother
OL,6,FShe is due to be sentenced at Swansea
OL,7,FCrown Court on Friday 25 April.
OL,9,FBruno Santos' daughter was a classmate
OL,10,Fof Alexander's at Whitestone Primary
OL,11,FSchool in West Cross. Bruno said he
OL,12,Fspoke with Alexander as the school
OL,13,Fbroke up for the summer holidays.
OL,15,F"Before the school holidays, we had a
OL,16,Fchance to talk with Alexander and he
OL,17,Fwas telling us about going to a theme
OL,18,Fpark in England and how much he
OL,19,Fenjoyed the rides and which ones were
OL,20,Fhis favourite," Bruno said.
