OL,4,Cto six-year-old killed by mother
OL,6,F"You could see he was a very bright
OL,7,Fand intelligent child."
OL,9,FBruno said his family, the school and
OL,10,Fthe local community were devastated by
OL,11,Fthe news of Alexander's death.
OL,13,FHe said: "It was quite a shock.
OL,15,F"Me and my wife were reading in the
OL,16,Fnews that something had happened, but
OL,17,Fwe didn't know who was involved until
OL,18,Fwe saw his face on the television.
