OL,6,F"It was a shock for everyone, for us,
OL,7,Fthe parents, the school and the
OL,8,Fteachers."
OL,10,FTo honour Alexander's memory, Bruno is
OL,11,Fundertaking the Yorkshire Three Peaks
OL,12,FChallenge next month to raise money to
OL,13,Fbuild a sensory garden at Whitestone
OL,14,FPrimary School.
OL,16,FThe challenge will see Bruno trek 24
OL,17,Fmiles and through 5,200 feet of
OL,18,Fascension.
