OL,6,FHe has raised #2,250 through a
OL,7,FJustGiving page, with all donations
OL,8,Falso being matched by his employer,
OL,9,FLloyd and White Community Broking.
OL,11,FBruno hopes the garden will help
OL,12,Fclassmates of Alexander's process
OL,13,Ftheir grief as well as keep his name
OL,14,Falive at the school.
OL,16,F"My wife spoke to one of the teachers,
OL,17,Fsaying it would be good to do
OL,18,Fsomething in memory of Alexander, like
OL,19,Fplanting a tree.
